Types of layouts for fxml: Pane,VBox,HBox,GridPane

Pane: When Things are added on the right side default is to add  it to the left corner
VBox: vertical box all items are aligned vertically down when added
HBox: horizontal box all items are aligned horizontally to right
Which of the following Container lays its children flexibly according to their absolute positioning? ->> Pane
Which of the following Container lays out its children in a single vertical column? ->>Vbox

Menu
The first child element of a MenuBar is ___________ ---->Menu --->MenuItem

